# Flycast Supabase & Realtime

**Table:** `flycast_messages` — columns: `id` (uuid), `text` (text), `created_at` (timestamptz), `updated_at` (timestamptz).

**Project:** Notical (ref: `sapnppmzywwuhqdiaicf`). Link with `supabase link --project-ref sapnppmzywwuhqdiaicf`.

**Shared hook:** `useRealtimeMessages` in `hooks/useRealtimeMessages.ts`:
- Fetches messages ordered by `created_at` desc on mount
- Subscribes to Supabase Realtime on `flycast_messages`
- On INSERT: prepend new message
- On UPDATE: update edited message in list
- Unsubscribe on unmount
- Returns `{ messages, connectionStatus }`

**Connection feedback:** Show "Reconnecting..." when `connectionStatus === 'disconnected'`.

**Migrations:** `supabase/migrations/`. Apply with `supabase db push`. Create with `supabase migration new <name>`.
